Title: Obstetric and Gynecologic Dermatology (With CDROM)
Author: এমব্রোস-রুড্‌ল্ফ
Summary:
Obstetric and Gynecologic Dermatology [With CDROM]
Offers you a practical guide for the evaluation, diagnosis, and management of a full range of common and uncommon obstetric and gynecologic skin disorders. This title includes more than 460 illustrations that emphasize pathologic and clinical appearances of dermatologic problems, providing visual guidance for the most informed diagnoses.
